0:21:30,000 --> 0:21:31,000
 because you can build it,

356
0:21:31,000 --> 0:21:33,000
 you can use it for yourself,

357
0:21:33,000 --> 0:21:37,000
 but you can't distribute it because in that moment you breached one of the licenses.

358
0:21:37,000 --> 0:21:44,000
 And this is a big problem with copyleft licenses especially.

